episodes.title: Clintons do not appear for Epstein testimony Comer threatens contempt
episodes.description:
Bill and Hillary Clinton declined to testify Tuesday before the Republican-led House Oversight Committee in its Jeffrey Epstein investigation, instead issuing a forceful letter to Chairman James Comer defending their refusal. 

https://thenationaldesk.com/news/americas-news-now/bill-hillary-clinton-refuse-to-testify-in-house-jeffrey-epstein-files-probe-as-house-oversight-committee-chairman-james-comer-threatens-contempt-charges-justice-department#
